TASK_DESCRIPTION=Two linked startup issues from Plan 22. Part A: Loading screen (doey-loading) hangs up to 120s — allKeyPanesReady() requires workers but they never reach BUSY because briefings are delayed. Fix: remove worker requirement, only need Boss+Taskmaster. Reduce timeout to 30-45s. Rebuild binary. Part B: Taskmaster receives briefing but becomes unresponsive to subsequent messages. Research the wait-loop entry and trigger detection on fresh startup. See plan at .doey/plans/22.md for full details.
TASK_SUBTASKS=1:Part A: Fix loading screen hang — dispatch to W3:done\n2:Part B: Fix Taskmaster wake loop — dispatch to W2:done\n3:W3.1: Fix allKeyPanesReady() + reduce timeout + rebuild binary:done\n4:W2.1: Research taskmaster-wait.sh trigger detection:done\n5:W2.2: Research doey msg send trigger file creation:done\n6:W2.1: Fix msgNudgePane — always send-keys to Taskmaster regardless of BUSY status:done\n7:W2.2: Fix Taskmaster agent template — enforce sleep loop re-entry after every response:done\n8:W2.3: Fix stop-status.sh — ensure Taskmaster status resets correctly + run bash compat test:done
